programme.title: Live Carabao Cup
programme.desc: Arsenal v Tottenham Hotspur (Kick-off 7.45pm). Coverage of the quarter-final match, which takes place at Emirates Stadium. This will be the second North London derby of the season, after the teams faced each other here in the Premier League 17 days ago. It's also the fifth time they have been drawn against each other in this competition since the turn of the century, and the Gunners will look to continue their winning record having dumped Spurs out of the competition on three of those occasions, most recently in 2015.

programme.desc: Crystal Palace v Watford. Action from the 2012/13 Championship play-off final at Wembley Stadium, as the teams contested a place in the top flight alongside the already promoted Cardiff City and Hull City. Palace reached this match when Wilfried Zaha scored a brace in a 2-0 away win against Brighton & Hove Albion after a goalless draw in the first leg. Meanwhile, Watford bounced back from narrowly missing out on automatic promotion by overcoming Leicester City in dramatic fashion, with Troy Deeney scoring an injury time-winner on the counter after Manuel Almunia had saved a penalty.

programme.title: KHL: Bars - Avtomobilist
programme.desc: S polnim imenom Kontinentalna hokejska liga za ligo NHL velja za drugo najmočnejšo hokejsko tekmovanje na svetu. Prvič so tekmovanje izvedeli leta 2008, večina sodelujočih klubov je iz Rusije, devetnajst, po en klub pa iz Belorusije, Latvije, Finske, Slovaške, Kazahstana in Kitajske. Naslov branijo člani Barsa iz Kazana.

programme.title: Spanish league: Real Madrid - Rayo Vallecano

programme.title: Evroliga - 13. Round: Anadolu Efes - Budučnost

programme.title: Champions League (m): ACH Volley - Zenit

Na prvi domači tekmi oranžni zmaji pričakujejo močni Zenit, ki je kot nosilec skupine prvi favorit za napredovanje v četrtfinale.

programme.title: Live! Champions League (ž): Fenerbahce - Chemik
programme.desc: V Ligi prvakinj se že več kot pol stoletja merijo najboljši ženski odbojkarski kolektivi iz stare celine. V tekmovanju nastopa 20 ekip, ki se sprva merijo v skupinah, nato pa tekmovanje poteka na izpadanje. Tekmovanje se zaključi z zaključnim turnirjem, na katerega se uvrstijo tri najboljša moštva iz »playoffa« in organizator turnirja.
